This generator has set up the following stack:

  1. Testing
    * RSpec
    * Capybara
    * Database Cleaner
    * SimpleCov
    * Guard
  2. Frontend
    * Bootstrap
    * Disabled Turbolinks
    * Google Analytics
    * Precompiled assets in production
  3. Gem groups set up for easy Heroku deployment
    * Postgres will work out of the box. No configuration necessary.

